Phase 2: Basic Validation (lines 4406-4437)
Three quick checks, each returning (False, "", 0) if failed:

Empty file check (line 4410) -- Rejects 0-byte files. A file with even 1 byte passes this gate.

Extension check (line 4418) -- Rejects anything that doesn't end in .csv.

Content validation (line 4427) -- Calls validate_file_content() which checks that the CSV has proper headers, rows, and structural integrity. Returns a list of validation errors if something is wrong.

Phase 3: Retailer Discovery (lines 4439-4452)

lambda_function.py
