            client_id, brand_name, status_logger=status_logger
        )
Queries the pipeline-infos DynamoDB table to get all retailers registered for this client+brand. This is the "source of truth" for which retailers exist.

If no retailers are found in DynamoDB, it falls back to a single-entry list using the retailer_id from the incoming event. It also ensures the event's retailer is in the list even if DynamoDB didn't return it.

